desc_short	-----								Super Arcade Football is a fast action, modern take on the classic football genre. Play singleplayer or with up to 4 friends locally, with intense scorelines, dynamic gameplay and crazy fun. No real-life simulation, no micro transactions, just pure arcade football action!							
